name: Censored AI
description: We're revolutionizing the digital experience in the world of cryptocurrency. Our team of passionate tech enthusiasts is dedicated to creating an AI-powered engine that facilitates seamless cryptocurrency swaps, ensuring efficient and secure transactions. The name "Censored AI" reflects our commitment to transparency and control, allowing users to manage their digital assets with confidence and precision. In addition to our swap engine, we are also developing an AI-powered chatbot that ensures safe, clean, and respectful online conversations by filtering out explicit content and providing accurate, helpful responses. We believe in making the crypto space more accessible and efficient for users of all experience levels.
